snippet.title: WDL Workflow Basics
snippet.description:
This video will give you a quick introduction to WDL Workflow Basics.

WDL Workflows Guide: https://jhudatascience.org/AnVIL_Book_WDL

Check out the Getting Started Guide here: https://jhudatascience.org/AnVIL_Book_Getting_Started/

AnVIL Help: https://help.anvilproject.org/

You can see the slides for this video here: https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1Dioe_Qd3hdJ0UAP4LA6gJsm07Lr1wRpax5FLYr6xU3M
